```Html

 <div class="box">
    <h2>Gradient Border</h2>
    <p>This uses the background + border-box trick.</p>
  </div>

```

``` Css

 .box {
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 10px solid transparent;
      padding: 20px;
      width: 300px;
      text-align: center;

      background:
        linear-gradient(#fff, #fff) padding-box,
        linear-gradient(45deg, #960E60, #ff6ec4) border-box;
    }

// Here you need to use background with double gradiant 
one for solid color other for border gradiant color with propeties like  
- padding-box with solid color and - border-box with border gradiant color 

```
